{"tid":648702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］未能共識 會計師公會核數師辭任核數師","createTime":"2018-05-01T02:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T16:20:33.000Z","uid":72280,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd24ba4aa9dead8dfa5592e999da3d6c3b31168","tid":648702,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"早前遭會員聯署公開派錢及要求解僱CEO 的會計師公會，其核數師瑪澤會計師事務所已辭任該公司核數師，即日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/101849_9e6618cbc5204f151aab52028348a6b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F101849_9e6618cbc5204f151aab52028348a6b7.png&h=190edecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會計師公會向會員發信，稱與沿用8年的核數師瑪澤會計師事務所，未能就截至今年6月底的財政年度和為2018年周年大會的核數服務達成共識，瑪澤已於3月23日起辭任。<br />\n<br />\n據指在辭任函中表示，經考慮審計費用水平、鑑於當前工作量而可動用的內部資源及審計相關專業風險後，因此作出辭任決定。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，大信梁學濂（香港）會計師事務所獲委任為新任會計師，自4月12日起生效，以填補瑪澤辭任後出現之臨時空缺，並留任直至公司下屆會員週年大會結束為止。"},{"pid":"d29f199693325966efd8ce11939ec61731b05e34","tid":648702,"uid":72280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n會計師公會的核數師辭職(resign)，電郵主題卻寫成更換(replacement)。如果他們認為兩個字無大分別並可以交替使用，我無話可說。仲有，點解核數師三月二十三日辭任，過左一個月，要等到找到繼任人才通知會員？<br />\n<br />\n之前唔係話個會有好多現金，點解核數師走得咁急？<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"74c0b257bb81b71766544e46a58552744cfef3fb","tid":648702,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f3d48b52559f5b7155dc81f610fd4e86a08024","tid":648702,"uid":5445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"成件事都好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5982029eff344f6c916b14794651dee8c17bbd4b","tid":648702,"uid":72280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0f3d48b52559f5b7155dc81f610fd4e86a08024","tid":648702,"uid":5445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"成件事都好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"有兩個問題<br />\n1.hkicpa 不是自稱坐擁數十億現金<br />\n點會因爲俾唔起Audit Fee 而迫走上任auditor <br />\n<br />\n2.之前公會唔係話所有服務合約要公開招標<br />\n點解今次唔見有公開競投招標出現？"},{"pid":"1133076cba7e5a907cbe8c549d8bfbf8a1a3ff22","tid":648702,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T17:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882c247b94eb4d7509a61abb070d63133b00d66e","tid":648702,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabc1a22f4df8497a9f5ae853de3cc7bd1944f02","tid":648702,"uid":98784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"通常話audit fee傾唔掂數都係籍口黎，你懂的"},{"pid":"9512bb18d0221d20c1f7fe34dd7e17e03169f17f","tid":648702,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"會計呢個行業...你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da1710e884c4a37eefc0d325d919ccadc67f336","tid":648702,"uid":52972,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5982029eff344f6c916b14794651dee8c17bbd4b","tid":648702,"uid":72280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0f3d48b52559f5b7155dc81f610fd4e86a08024","tid":648702,"uid":5445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"成件事都好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"有兩個問題<br />\n1.hkicpa 不是自稱坐擁數十億現金<br />\n點會因爲俾唔起Audit Fee 而迫走上任auditor <br />\n<br />\n2.之前公會唔係話所有服務合約要公開招標<br />\n點解今次唔見有公開競投招標出現？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:49:23.000Z","msg":"師兄有所不知， 核數師辭職， 永遠都係用&ldquo;audit fee&rdquo; 呢個理由<img 